I can recompile it and run it for a bit.  What debug options would be
useful for this?
When I had it enabled I had this:
# CONFIG_NOHIGHMEM is not set
CONFIG_HIGHMEM4G=y
# CONFIG_HIGHMEM64G is not set
CONFIG_HIGHMEM=y
CONFIG_HIGHPTE=y
Thus spake Zan Lynx (zlynx@acm.org):
